# Per-language encoder outputs are EPHEMERAL verification artifacts, regenerated
# by each PSM's runner and diffed against the single source of truth (*.golden.bin)
# by verify.sh. The WIRE is the wire: there is ONE golden per (feature, repr), not
# one per language. See CANONICAL.md.
*.rust.bin
*.cpp.bin
*.python.bin
*.java.bin
*.ts.bin
*.c.bin
*.csharp.bin

